Urbal = urban + rural (ruralising urbaninity, instead of 'rurban' which is the influence of cities on the rural)

Example, video the [[Urbal Fix]], at http://www.turnstone.tv/tuf1.html : "The Urbal Fix is a necessarily holistic urban sustainability concept, 
developed by Tom Bliss while studying for an MA at Leeds Metropolitan University (Bliss 2010)."


